data.meta_description: We found 1,200+ words and phrases that rhyme with embarrassment: abandonment · abatement · abridgement · accompaniment · accomplishment · accouterment · accoutrement · achievement · acknowledgement · acknowledgment
data.text:
What the Table Columns Mean

Word: A word that rhymes with embarrassment.

Rhyming Percentage: How closely the word rhymes with embarrassment. A 100 means perfect rhyme while an 80 or 90 means a close rhyme. When this column says "Slant Rhyme," the word only rhymes if said in a certain way.

Syllables: The number of syllables in the word.

Type: The type of word.
